  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking for an immersive VR physics puzzler? Chrono Weaver is a single-player co-op game. Work with copies of yourself as you travel through space and time, finding solutions to seemingly impossible tests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>… So human, Are you a team player even when you’re all by yourself?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2053370/extras/WithFriendsLong.GIF?t=1737765730\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>… Do you love working in a rapidly changing environment?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2053370/extras/backandforth.GIF?t=1737765730\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>… If this sounds like you, read more to find out how The Company can help give your life purpose!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EMPLOYMENT APPLICATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JOB TITLE:</strong> Data Integrity Engineer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOURS:</strong> Unknown</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PAY:</strong> Unlikely</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOB REQUIREMENTS:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooperate with yourself across space and time, everything revolves around you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your wits to discover the puzzling path to the data disk</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demonstrate your accuracy and precision with the amazing Quantum Slingshot</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EMPLOYEE BENEFITS:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Priceless mentorship from your amazing supervisor who definitely does <strong>NOT</strong> look like a flying trashcan</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2053370/extras/booootrash.GIF?t=1737765730\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover that collaborating with your co-workers can be a smashing good time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2053370/extras/BounceShot_02.GIF?t=1737765730\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work in one of the most beautifully productive environments on the planet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2053370/extras/SecurityCam.GIF?t=1737765730\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What do you say? Apply today. You’re the only one standing in your way.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2053370/extras/slogan.GIF?t=1737765730\" /></span></p>",
